                                sourceEvent.eventName
                              } ${isPrimary ? "üì¶" : "üè∑Ô∏è"}</span>`
                            : `<span style="color: #e74c3c; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-left: 8px;">‚ö† Event "${eventName}" not found or field not in payload</span>`
                        }
                      </div>
                      <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #657786;">
